headline: Reflecting On Gas and Liquid Handling Stocks’ Q3 Earnings: Ingersoll Rand (NYSE:IR)
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q3. Today, we are looking at gas and liquid handling stocks, starting with Ingersoll Rand (NYSE:IR).
